				\begin{document}$$-{e}^{2}/(3h)$$\end{document}−e2/(3h), labeled −1/3, leading to a conductance 4/3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
