The measurements are performed on a two-dimensional electron gas made in high mobility GaAs/Ga(Al)As heterojunction with electron density ns = 1.11 1015 m−2 and zero field mobility μ = 300 m2 V−1 s−1, see SM. The filling factor ν = 2/3 occurs at field B\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
